# playwright
/playwright-report/
/test-results/
/playwright/.cache/

# Google / Firebase — google-services.json is NOT secret (ships in every APK,
# decompilable from any installed build) and must be tracked so EAS Build can
# find it. The Firebase service-account JSON (used for FCM V1 push) IS secret
# and is uploaded via `eas credentials`, not via the repo.

# (devenv / direnv now live at the repo root; see top-level .gitignore)
